                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-485-18610610 t18610610-485-punishment-32"></join>Confined Twelve Months</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">COLLINS</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18610610-485-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
